{
  "texts": [
    "For each scenario, we monitor certain indicators that signify progress to-wards the scenario's objectives, such as blocks, ingredients or triggers.",
    "The completion rate is calculated based on the quantity of these indicators, providing a measure of how much of the scenario has been completed defined in AppendixA.",
    "The formula for calculating the completion rate is as follows:",
    "# Indicators Detected # Total Indicators Expected Efficiency of Completion (E).",
    "It is defined as the ratio of the task completion rate to the actual time taken by the agents."
  ]
}